=====================================================================
After the Gate 3 choice: rewrite the three fire holds (Eastmarch,
Throat, Whiterun) per the runsheet ## 11 matrix -- party fire resolved,
Krusp's fire won-with-attrition, ignored fire escalated. After the
Dragonstone: fire the Tier 2 beat (Fort Dunstad falls; Pale entry and
